title: Chimpan A
description:
A Traveler Lost in Time
A Poet Adrift in Space
A Pirate Guided by Her Heart
A Man Rescued by Love.


Cyberpunk hiphop ballads with urban poetry 
(and a timey-wimey love story)
Next Stop Everywhere!

Format: FLAC / cue, 44.1k Hz, Stereo
Bitrate: 778kbps
Length: 1:22:24
Tracks: 13

Custom cover art, cd label, and printable art sleeve included (pdf).

Further Out Than Anyone 

So is this progressive rock then? 
Well, it certainly isn't rock, but it sure as hell is very progressive. 
And if you agree that the pioneers of electronic music like Tangerine Dream 
and Kraftwerk or instrumentalists like Mike Oldfield are to be considered prog, 
then Chimpan A firmly belongs in the same genre. 
This special remix has sci-fi sound effects and tv soundclips,
spacey beat poetry, and even some space aliens.
